data.description: Discover the largest home for sale in the sought-after NorthBrook Community at an incredible new price! This expansive 4-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom home offers a wealth of living space, making it a must-see opportunity. Step inside to be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, featuring a spacious family room with an electric fireplace and vaulted ceilings, a generously sized kitchen with freshly painted cabinets and island seating, a formal living room, formal dining room, den, and a versatile room ideal for a home office or children's playroom on the main level. Upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits with a beautiful en suite, accompanied by two bedrooms sharing a Jack and Jill bathroom, and another bedroom with its own access to a hall bathroom – offering convenience and privacy for all.  But this house doesn't end there. The finished basement presents a wealth of possibilities, including a large bonus room, a rec room, a full bathroom, a potential 5th bedroom, and an unfinished room perfect for storage. Walk out to the beautiful backyard, complete with a custom paver patio and fire pit, creating an ideal outdoor retreat. While the seller has recently refreshed the kitchen cabinets and completed repairs, the home is ready for a touch of TLC to unlock its full potential. With a little love, this property is poised to become the perfect home for its new owner.
